    "QuantumMob/Q3", "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "GivensFactor[op] returns a list of controlled-unitary and single-qubit \
gates that compose the unitary operator op. GivensFactor[mat, {s1, s2, ...}] \
factorizes the unitary operator acting on qubits s$1,s$2,$$ the matrix \
representation of which is given by the unitary matrix mat. GivensFactor[mat] \
returns a list of Givens rotation matrices that compose the unitary matrix \
mat. The first element of the returned the global factor.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "GivensFactor", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
